# This is a placeholder file for the Excel template
# The actual Excel file would be created using PhpSpreadsheet library
# Users should download this template to understand the required format

Required columns for laptop models import:
1. برند (Brand)
2. مدل (Model) 
3. سال عرضه (Release Year)
4. قیمت پایه (Base Price)
5. CPU پایه (Base CPU)
6. RAM پایه (Base RAM)
7. GPU پایه (Base GPU)
8. Storage پایه (Base Storage)

Sample data:
Dell,XPS 13,2020,45000000,Intel Core i7-1065G7,16GB,Intel UHD Graphics,512GB SSD
Apple,MacBook Pro 13,2021,55000000,Apple M1,8GB,Apple M1 GPU,256GB SSD
Lenovo,ThinkPad X1 Carbon,2019,35000000,Intel Core i5-8265U,8GB,Intel UHD Graphics 620,256GB SSD